 Seek refuge in Allah from darkness as it settles","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, looked at the moon and he said, \u201cO Aisha, seek refuge in Allah from the evil of this, for this is \u2018the darkness when it settles.\u2019\u201d (113:3) Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3366 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32817,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/16\/prophet-more-handsome-qamar\/","url_meta":{"origin":32792,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet more handsome than the moon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, on a clear night while he was wearing a red cloak. I turned my sight between him and the moon and, to me, he was more handsome and beautiful than the moon. Source: al-Shama\u0304\u2019il\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/prophet-face-like-qamar\/","url_meta":{"origin":32792,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet&#8217;s face wa